These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, sprite
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, artichoke, mango, cherry
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, snowmobile, subway, van
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the person drinking cola is the person eating pomegranate##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person eating mango##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
7. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | fanta  | sprite | mirinda    | cola       |
| Food         | artichoke | cherry    | mango      | pomegranate |
| Transport   | bike   | subway | snowmobile | van        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, broccoli, corn, pear
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, pink, white, black
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who likes black##1
2. the person eating pear is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who likes white is on the right of the person eating corn##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the bike is the person who likes lavender##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | corn   | broccoli | asparagus     | pear      |
| Color         | pink | white | black | lavender |
| Transport   | car    | roller   | motorbike     | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, rock-climbing, singing, video-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, hip-hop, pop
City: london, miami, liverpool, paris
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | gardening | rock-climbing | singing | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | electronic    | country | hip-hop     |
| City   | london | liverpool    | paris | miami    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, aquamarine, ivory, azure
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, soccer, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, taxi, train
1. the person who likes ivory is the person driving the train##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who likes ivory##1
7. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
8. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Color         | lavender | azure | ivory | aquamarine |
| Sport       | rugby     | volleyball      | rowing     | soccer      |
| Transport   | motorbike | jet-ski         | train      | taxi        |

