.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, horror, mystery, satire
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, pink, orange, apricot
1. the accountant is the person who likes pink##1
2. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the writer##1
4. the person who likes apricot is on the far left##1
5. the designer is on the far left##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is the mechanic##1
7. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
8. the writer is the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | designer | mechanic | writer | accountant |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | mystery  | horror | disaster   |
| Color   | apricot   | black     | orange | pink       |

