.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, photographer, social-worker, videographer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, volleyball, weightlifting
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, turkish, argentine, pakistani
1. the australian is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the photographer##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the pakistani is on the right of the turkish##1
6. the australian is on the left of the videographer##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is the argentine##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Job         | bartender  | videographer | photographer  | social-worker |
| Sport       | volleyball | rugby        | weightlifting | cricket       |
| Nationality   | australian   | turkish          | pakistani          | argentine       |

