4. the person eating lime is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
5. the person eating radish is on the right of the fan of metal##1
6. the person eating lime is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling | chess    | baking        | reading |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | rock     | trance        | blues   |
| Food         | pineapple   | radish | lime | watermelon  |

