The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, fantasy, superhero, thriller
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, horse, rabbit
1. the cottage house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the townhouse house is the owner of the horse##1
5. the cottage house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the futuristic house##1
7. the futuristic house is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| House          | craftsman     | cottage   | futuristic | townhouse |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | thriller | superhero | fantasy   |
| Pet           | rabbit    | fish     | bird      | horse     |

