4. the fan of funk is the person who likes yellow##1
5. the lawyer is on the far left##1
6. the scientist is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
7. the person who likes turquise is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Job           | lawyer  | architect | bartender  | scientist |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | d&b       | electronic | punk      |
| Color   | yellow | amber  | lavender    | turquise    |

