.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, dahlia, bellflower, daisy
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, nigerian, pakistani, russian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, parkour, tennis
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
4. the pakistani is on the far right##1
5. the indonesian is the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the russian is on the far left##1
7. the person who growsdaisy is on the far right##1
8. the russian is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Flower           | dahlia  | bellflower  | zinnia | daisy |
| Nationality   | russian   | indonesian | nigerian   | pakistani      |
| Sport         | badminton | parkour    | biathlon   | tennis         |

 